page / title "Home"
  "Welcome to Kilnx."
  "The backend language for the htmx era."

page /about title "About"
  "Kilnx is a declarative backend language written in Go."
  "It pairs natively with htmx."
  "29 keywords. Single binary. Zero dependencies."

page /principles title "Principles"
  "The complexity is the tool's fault, not the problem's."
  "Zero decisions before the first useful line."
  "SQL is a first-class citizen."
  "HTML is the native output."
  "The binary is the deploy."
